<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634127375097262049" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634127380382764626">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>The example contains two <em>ListBoxes </em>and four buttons. <em> ListBoxes </em>have <em>MultiExtended </em>selection mode. The buttons are the follwing: <br />'&gt;' &ndash; transfer selected items from left <em>ListBox </em>to right ListBox; <br />'&gt;&gt;' &ndash; transfer all items from left <em>ListBox </em>to right ListBox; <br />'&lt;' - transfer selected items from right <em>ListBox </em>to left <em>ListBox</em>; <br />'&lt;&lt;' &ndash; transfer all items from right <em>ListBox </em>to left <em>ListBox</em>.</p><p>Select items in the one of the <em>ListBoxes </em>and click on one of the buttons for transferring items to another <em>ListBox</em>.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>ListBox </em>stores its items in the Items collection of the <em>ListBox</em>.<em>ObjectCollection </em>type. For working with <em>ListBox </em>items we should use methods of the collection. Changes in the Items collection will be represented in the owner <em>ListBox</em>. To transfer items from one <em>ListBox </em>to another there is used the following methods of the items collection:<br /><em>AddRange </em>&ndash; adds array items into the Items collection;<br /><em>Add </em>&ndash; adds array item into the Items collection;<br /><em>Remove </em>&ndash; removes item from the Items collection;<br /><em>Clear </em>&ndash; remove all elements of the Items collection.<br />To get selection items ListBox contains the following property:<br /><em>SelectedIndex </em>&ndash; defines the zero-based index of the currently selected item in a <em>ListBox</em>;<br /><em>SelectedIndices </em>- defines a collection that contains the zero-based indexes of all currently selected items in the <em>ListBox</em>;<br /><em>SelectedItem </em>&ndash; defines the currently selected item in the <em>ListBox</em>.<br /><em>SelectedItems </em>&ndash; defines a collection containing the currently selected items in the <em>ListBox</em>.</p><p>The Visual WebGui <em>ListBox </em>fires <em>SelectedIndexChanged </em>event when the <em>SelectedIndex </em>property has changed.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
